```{% dnd_section
  max_width=1536,
  padding={
    "default" : {
      "top" : "0pc"
    },
    "mobile" : {
      "bottom" : "40px"
    }
  }
%}
  {% dnd_column
    offset=0,
    width=6
  %}
    {% dnd_row %}
      {% dnd_module
        path="Path of your image module",
        offset=0,
        width=12,
        image={
          "alt" : "Untitled-1200x720-2",
          "height" : 720,
          "loading" : "lazy",
          "max_height" : 720,
          "max_width" : 1200,
          "size_type" : "auto",
          "src" : "Image path",
          "width" : 1200
        }
      %}
      {% end_dnd_module %}
    {% end_dnd_row %}
  {% end_dnd_column %}
  {% dnd_column
    offset=6,
    width=6,
    padding={
      "mobile" : {
        "top" : "20px"
      }
    }
  %}
    {% dnd_row %}
      {% dnd_module
        path="Path of your richtext module",
        offset=0,
        width=12
      %}
        {% module_attribute "richtext" %}
          &lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Find Out what this cat is looking at&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
          &lt;p&gt;We honestly don't currently understand what this car is looking at. It could be a small insect. It could be an errant carpet fiber. Perhaps the cat is looking at nothing and pondering deep existential questions that have haunted us all at on time or another.&lt;/p&gt;
          &lt;p&gt;We may never know. But we will never stop trying to find the answer.&lt;/p&gt;
        {% end_module_attribute %}
      {% end_dnd_module %}
    {% end_dnd_row %}
  {% end_dnd_column %}
{% end_dnd_section %}```
Make sure you add the layout.css file from boilerplate, otherwise grid will not working.

Let me know if you still facing the issue.
